        Creating a person with an ID, associated user name, first name, last name, gender, and possible father, mother, and spouse ID
        Parameters:
        personID - the ID of the person
        associatedUserName - the associated name to which the person belongs
        firstName - the first name of the person
        lastName - the last name of the person
        gender - the gender of the person
        fatherID - the father's ID of the person, if possible
        motherID - the mother's ID of the person, if possible
        spouseID - the spouse's ID of the person, if possible
